          "type": "remove",
          "lineNumber": 43,
          "content": "- 50 HP Gimmighoul is not worth it! It is a huge liability in so many situations, even though Call for Family is sometimes good. I did include some stuff about 50 HP Gimmi in the matchup notes because most people play it."
